        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>237 S Deplaines St.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><placeName>Chicago, Ill.</placeName>, <date>19 March
                1867</date></p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I trust you will not misconstrue my words<lb/> and ascribe to me
                false motives, if I respectfully<lb/> ask you to discontinue sending the
                Occident<lb/> to me.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">My office is a very poorly paid one, and I<lb/> cannot help it, I
                    <hi rend="underline">must</hi> re<add>?</add> it in every<lb/> way possible.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I shall nevertheless continue to read the Occident.<lb/> Being a
                member of the “Young men's ass'n” here, which<lb/> keeps your periodical in its
                reading room, I<lb/> shall not miss the opportunity to read the<lb/> same.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I appreciate fully the decency and dignity of<lb/> your paper, and
                the honesty and straightfor<lb/>wardness with which it is conducted. Would</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>to God, <hi rend="underline">all</hi> our Jewish papers would in the<lb/> same manner
                be decent and honest.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Not knowing exactly what balance I owe you,<lb/> I would ask you to
                let me know the amount<lb/> due you, and I shall hasten to pay my balance.<lb/>
                <add>מעתה אדוני אל נא ידע בעיניך ואל תשת עלי חטאתי כי כתבתי לך את הדברים האלה.
                    אך</add></p>
            <p>I remain, my dear sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">yours, very respectfully,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">B. Felsenthal</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
    </text>
